<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="icon" href="logos/plicon.png" type="images/x-icon" width="400" height="400">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Calistoga&family=Josefin+Sans:ital,wght@0,100..700;1,100..700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>SignUp</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        a:active {
            transform: scale(0.9);
        }
    </style>
</head>


<body style="width: 100vw; background-color: goldenrod;">
    <header style="height: 10vh; width: 100vw; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
        <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: bold; ">
            <h1 style="font-weight: 900; font-size: 1.5rem; color: rgb(67, 5, 67); font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif;">Xtream</h1>
            <span><img src="logos/plicon.png" alt="" width="40" height="40"></span>
            <h1 style="font-weight: 900; font-size: 1.5rem; color: rgb(67, 5, 67); font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif;">League</h1>
        </div>

    </header>

    <main style="width: 100vw; height: 90vh; padding: 10px; background-color: goldenrod; display: flex; flex-flow: column nowrap; align-items: center; justify-content: flex-start;">
        
        <section class="description" style="width: 95%; height: 60%; display: flex; flex-flow: column nowrap; justify-content: flex-start; align-items: center; border-radius: 30px 30px 10px 10px; background-image: linear-gradient(-45deg, white, yellow, gold, goldenrod, gold, yellow, white); box-shadow: 0 5px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3), 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.29);">
            <div style="height: 20%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                <h1 style="color: purple; font-size: 1.45rem; font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: bold;">Welcome to Fantasy Bets</h1>
            </div>
            <div style="height: 20%; padding-inline: 20px; display: flex; flex-flow: column nowrap; justify-content: center; align-items: center;" >
                <p style="color: green; font-weight: bold; font-family:'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;">The official fantasy football competitions of the Premier League</p>
                <p style="color: green; font-weight: bold; font-size: .95rem; font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;">Compete with Other Fpl Managers each GW and Earn</p>
            </div>
            <div style="height: 40%; padding-inline: 20px; display: flex; flex-flow: column nowrap; justify-content: flex-start; align-items: center;">
                    <h2 style="height: 20%; color: purple; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 900; font-family: cursive; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 10px;">Features</h2>
                    <p style="height: 20%; color: green; font-weight: bold; font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: .95rem; text-align: center;">Place Head to Head bets with other Fpl Managers</p>
                    <p style="height: 20%; color: green; font-weight: bold; font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: .95rem; text-align: center;">Join parties and compete with multiple Fpl Managers</p>
                    <p style="height: 20%; color: green; font-weight: bold; font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: .95rem; text-align: center;">See Premier League statistics for players and teams</p>
                    <p style="height: 20%; color: green; font-weight: bold; font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: .95rem; text-align: center;">Access leaderboards for Fpl managers for best teams</p>
                  
            </div>
            
             <div style="height: 20%; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;">
                <p style="text-align: center; font-weight: bold; color: purple; font-size: 1.1rem; font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif;">Sign in and Register your Fpl team to play</p>
             </div>
              
        </section>

        <section class="google" style="height: 8vh; width: 95%; margin-top: 30px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; ">
             <a href="/auth/google" class="google-btn" style="text-decoration: none;  display: flex; height: 80%; width: 280px; border-radius: 40px; background-color: white; box-shadow: 0 5px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3), 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.29);">
               <div class="icon " style="height: 100%; width: 20%; border-radius: 40px 0 0 40px; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;">
                <img src="/logos/google.png" alt="" width="40" height="40">
               </div>
               <div class="google-desrp" style="height: 100%; width: 80%; border-radius: 0 40px 40px 0; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;">
                 <p class="sign" style="color: purple; text-align: center; font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: bolder; font-family: 'Lucida Sans', 'Lucida Sans Regular', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;" >Sign in with Google</p> 
               </div>
            </a>     
        </section>
        <section style="height: 20%; width: 100%; margin-top: 20px; background-color: transparent; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;">
            <img src="logos/plicon.png" alt="" width="100" height="100px">
        </section>


    </main>

    
      
    
</body>
</html>